nodes.text: At some point during the reign of the Galactic Empire, an Imperial captain hired the droid bounty hunter IG-88 to apprehend a thief who had managed to highjack a Lambda-class T-4a shuttle on a jungle world. The droid managed to disable the thief, identifying him as Venga Liss, son of the crime lord over the Gillanium Syndicate. Calculating the Aqualish to be worth nothing to it, IG-88 killed Liss by deploying a thermal detonator into the shuttle, destroying it, much to the captain's dismay.
